WEBVTT

1
00:00:03.320 --> 00:00:05.040
The Barclays app

2
00:00:05.080 --> 00:00:07.480
How to register on an Android device

3
00:00:07.480 --> 00:00:09.760
Once you've downloaded the app
from your app store,

4
00:00:09.840 --> 00:00:11.760
it's really easy to get started.

5
00:00:11.960 --> 00:00:13.960
Tap on 'Register for the app'.

6
00:00:16.080 --> 00:00:19.600
Next, you'll need to enter
a 5-digit passcode

7
00:00:19.600 --> 00:00:21.440
and re-enter to confirm.

8
00:00:23.160 --> 00:00:26.000
Read through the terms and conditions
and if you're happy,

9
00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:27.480
tap to accept them.

10
00:00:28.240 --> 00:00:30.760
If you've not received
an activation code,

11
00:00:30.760 --> 00:00:33.160
tap 'No, continue without'.

12
00:00:34.240 --> 00:00:39.120
Next, select 'Barclay's UK
Current Account' and tap 'Continue'.

13
00:00:40.480 --> 00:00:43.120
Now to register, you'll need a mobile number,

14
00:00:43.120 --> 00:00:46.000
your Barclays debit card
and your card PIN

15
00:00:47.400 --> 00:00:49.720
If you have them, tap 'Continue'.

16
00:00:50.920 --> 00:00:53.320
Tap 'No'.

17
00:00:53.640 --> 00:00:59.520
Then, to use your contactless Visa card to
register for the app, select 'Tap My Card'.

18
00:00:59.560 --> 00:01:04.760
Place your card so it touches the back
of your phone and move it up and down.

19
00:01:05.680 --> 00:01:10.760
Once your card details have been scanned,
they'll appear on your screen like this.

20
00:01:10.800 --> 00:01:12.200
Tap 'Continue'.

21
00:01:15.160 --> 00:01:18.240
Enter your mobile number, tap 'Done'.

22
00:01:20.080 --> 00:01:22.080
Then tap 'Continue'.

23
00:01:23.440 --> 00:01:26.440
Enter again to confirm
and tap 'Done'.

24
00:01:27.440 --> 00:01:29.200
Followed by 'Continue'.

25
00:01:31.400 --> 00:01:33.440
Once your details have been confirmed,

26
00:01:33.440 --> 00:01:36.520
you'll need to enter your PIN
for the debit card you entered.

27
00:01:37.200 --> 00:01:38.560
Tap 'Continue',

28
00:01:39.400 --> 00:01:43.360
then enter a meaningful word
to welcome you each time you log in,

29
00:01:43.360 --> 00:01:46.040
so you'll know you're using
the genuine app.

30
00:01:46.240 --> 00:01:47.600
Tap 'Continue'.

31
00:01:49.040 --> 00:01:52.400
And that's it -
your registration will be complete.

32
00:01:53.120 --> 00:01:57.040
You'll now be able to use biometric login,
if available, on your device,

33
00:01:57.080 --> 00:02:01.120
review your notification preferences
and take a tour of the app.

